# Local DB + uploads backups (never commit).
# NOTE: leading slash anchors to the repo root ONLY — a bare 'backups/' also matched
# source dirs like app/app/admin/backups and app/app/api/**/backups, silently
# excluding the entire DR/backups feature from git + CI. Keep it anchored.
/backups/
